title: Shell's Arctic oil search ends in failure with dry Alaskan well
text: Oil and Gas Shell's Arctic oil search ends in failure with dry Alaskan well Anglo Dutch company forced to suspend Alaskan oil search after exploration well finds little oil in the Chukchi Sea Shell is pulling out of Alaska Photo: REUTERS/Jason Redmond By Andrew Critchlow , Commodities editor 7:22AM BST 28 Sep 2015
